long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tap Supermarket is a game where you own your own supermarket and earn money by serving customers quickly, keeping products in stock and expanding your store.

A large supermarket has appeared in our city, and you will become its manager in charge of literally everything. You should also expand the product range by purchasing additional shelves and filling them up to the top. Make sure all products are placed; Don't let buyers line up at checkout. Help your customers leave the supermarket happy to grow your supermarket empire. Can you turn your small grocery store into a mega market?

How To Play:

Click on the cashier to get money. They are necessary for the purchase of goods, for the filling of warehouses. If you see an empty shelf or hanger, press the button and the movers will bring the goods. Let your store be full of customers at Tap Supermarket, and the products will never run out.


Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Tap Supermarket food game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
